title: Fox.Start
body:
<<if visited("Fox.Start") is false>>
Norra: Hi.
Fox: Hello.
Norra: . . . 
Fox: Can I help you with something?
Fox: It's just in the middle of some rather important business.
--> What are you working on? Can I help?
    Fox: No, it's foxy business. Move along. [[Fox.Exit]]
--> Okay, sorry to bother you. 
    [[Fox.Exit]]
<<else>>
Fox: Oh, it's you again.
[[Fox.Talk]]
<<endif>>

title: Fox.Talk
body:
Fox: I'm still rather busy.
--> You're just walking around.
    Fox: Like I said, fox business.
--> I need some help.
    Fox: What do I look like, your fairy godmother?
Fox: Run along a play.
[[Fox.Exit]]
